title: Is the Akali hoodie for real?
body:
Like I get basic-ass hoodies are going to cost $65 no matter what--even though some personalities/companies might still sell them as low as $35 (very rare, of course)--but what's with the R keycap?
https://truedamage.com/products/true-damage-ultimate-key-r

No design on back...more is less, I guess? Idk, feel like it is $55 at best XD what yall think?
